Team Deathmatch with 2 Teams 8 players each. First to 100 points wins.

Hop in your trusty vehicle with the squad and gear up to fight in a big city arena.

Only one team can emerge the winner amongst the chaos!

Tags: team deathmatch, squad

Original Map Name: Red/Green/Yellow/Purple - Car Fight

This FFA showdown has received a big update!

Harvest resources to level up, trade for gold, craft weapons and build your private island.

Do you have what it takes to top the leaderboards?

Tags: role playing, open world, survival, base

Original Map Name: SKYLAND (SAVING UPDATE!)

Compete in a four-round bracket squad battle! The team with the most eliminations at the end of the round moves on. The team that wins the 4th round wins the match!  Loadouts are randomized for both teams each round!

Respawn and Ammo Regeneration is ON and looting is OFF.

A competitive mode, designed to be intense whether you’re cranking 90’s or hiding in a bush.

Earn Hype by achieving placements or eliminating opponents. As you gain Hype, you’ll compete against tougher opponents with a similar skill level.

Travel to new islands and explore unique biomes to collect exotic fish! 

Bring your catches back to the museum to save them to your collection.

Upgrade your rod, battle with opponents, unlock special abilities, and use baits or hooks to become the ultimate fishing master!

Tags: collection, economy, exploration, tycoon

Original Map Name: Tide Tycoon Fishing! | PWR

A classic Prop Hunt game with a twist. Explore the modern mall and find the best spot to hide.

If you're eliminated as a Prop, you'll respawn on the Hunter team.

Listen carefully as a Hunter. The prop team gives off a noise every fifteen seconds!


Tags: prop hunt

Original Map Name:  Prop Hunt - Modern Mall - 50 Players

Jump into your own Battle Royale island and set the rules! Select from favorite LTM loot pools, set up combat scenarios with the new Bot Grenades, and create your own mode by setting options like gravity and fall damage. Fill your game with up to 15 friends on your own island, or matchmake with default options in a public Battle Lab.

A competitive mode, designed to be intense whether you’re cranking 90’s or hiding in a bush.

Earn Hype by achieving placements or eliminating opponents. As you gain Hype, you’ll compete against tougher opponents with a similar skill level.

Monsters have taken over the city! Earn gold by clearing them out.

Make sure to stop by the shop to upgrade your gear. If you look around you can even find loot.

Team up with others or survive on your own in this open world city.

Tags: open world, survival, creatures, role playing
